narratives.question_text: What knowledge, skills, and insights did you develop by taking this course?
comments: I partook in a series of conversations with Molly and my classmate Hazal in which we discussed the American landscape of the desert in connection with our work.

narratives.question_text: What are the strengths and weaknesses of this course and how could it be improved?
comments: The level of discussion and feedback was excellent. The one thing I would say was that it was too hard for us to secure studio space for the class at the beginning of the semester.

narratives.question_text: Would you recommend this course to another student? Please explain.
comments: It is a one-time independent project, so I can't recommend this one specifically, but I would definitely recommend creating an independent project in general.
